{"tid":1004922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"娶妻只為淫狎對方兒子 孌童癖：愛他愛得發狂","createTime":"2019-02-01T21:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T08:55:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e989faadbad0c7153a42284d028dd88ae6b3bc4","tid":1004922,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T21:41:24.000Z","msg":"澳洲一名孌童癖多年來向不少男童下手，更變態得為了可狎玩看中的男童，主動結識對方母親甚至與其中一位結婚，令人心寒。<br />\n這名52歲的孌童癖在1998年至2011年間先後性侵多名男童，直至其中一對受害兄弟長大後報案，警方才得以在前年將他繩之於法。他作供時承認找到目標後，會主動結識他們的母親並交往，從而得到淫辱男童的機會。<br />\n他向警方承認迎娶現任妻子完全是為了性侵她的兒子，更坦言對繼子「完全愛得發狂」。他指繼子與親生父親關係欠佳，令他有機可乘，更告訴對方兩人可以有性接觸，「因為這是父親與兒子該做的事」。男童信以為真，結果任由他侵犯，有一次妻子發現兩人在房中拉扯，幾乎揭發他的獸行，不過父子卻否認有任何不恰當行為。<br />\n孌童癖又承認曾性侵在昆士蘭省陽光海岸一個體育會認識的兩兄弟，最後兩童報警揭發事件。他表示自己10歲起便開始向其他男童下手，但不知為何會這樣做，他被控17項強姦罪，最終判囚15年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190202/59208165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190202%2F59208165&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=2966f231\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190202%2F59208165&h=cadf7f66\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190202/59208165</a>"},{"pid":"7755be58e2b59fc0f1ee114dd7956f5406704899","tid":1004922,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T22:12:50.000Z","msg":"愛上12歲女童！變態男竟勾引爸爸&hellip;再色誘媽媽<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/chzPxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/chzPxS</a>"},{"pid":"e3b47d906d80837066607b9fee61bbee2c1683e1","tid":1004922,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7755be58e2b59fc0f1ee114dd7956f5406704899","tid":1004922,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T22:12:50.000Z","msg":"愛上12歲女童！變態男竟勾引爸爸&hellip;再色誘媽媽<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/chzPxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/chzPxS</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"睇嚟幾十年前d孌童癖鍾意咁樣嚟得到細路"},{"pid":"28433e5f48f88f9c5f6752bdd87b8c1ceed1f1ea","tid":1004922,"uid":20405,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"睇左成篇文都冇講男人定女人<br />\n乜撚野叫一名戀童癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蘋果d 記者抄可能仲好d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabc91c6e433d91f8e5fa2834caf254d6425a201","tid":1004922,"uid":20405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28433e5f48f88f9c5f6752bdd87b8c1ceed1f1ea","tid":1004922,"uid":20405,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"睇左成篇文都冇講男人定女人<br />\n乜撚野叫一名戀童癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蘋果d 記者抄可能仲好d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">孌</span></span>"},{"pid":"461fab45ca3a41720ac66d7e65964c296d4dab57","tid":1004922,"uid":143288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28433e5f48f88f9c5f6752bdd87b8c1ceed1f1ea","tid":1004922,"uid":20405,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"睇左成篇文都冇講男人定女人<br />\n乜撚野叫一名戀童癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蘋果d 記者抄可能仲好d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"他"},{"pid":"6fa78162f12bcdb5887308f18d3e5198523fe25b","tid":1004922,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-0